# Formspree form IDs — the part after /f/ in your form's endpoint
# (e.g. an endpoint https://formspree.io/f/abcdwxyz  ->  ID is "abcdwxyz").
# Create two forms at https://formspree.io, then set the IDs here (.env.local)
# and in your Vercel project's Environment Variables.
FORMSPREE_CONTACT_ID=
FORMSPREE_NEWSLETTER_ID=
